title: "nickelate.sc: Vol. 1, No. 1 — Bilayer nickelate screening corpus"
message: >-
  If you use this corpus, screening interface, or curated schema, please cite
  the archived release. For any specific scientific claim, also cite the
  primary literature linked from each record.
