  - curated dataset
  - epitaxial strain
  - applied pressure
abstract: >-
  A pseudonymous, manually curated screening notebook over the published
  bilayer-nickelate superconductivity literature. Includes 23 measurements
  (ambient films, films under applied pressure, bulk under pressure), a
  22-gate physical/control/evidence schema, gap candidates derived as
  Hamming-distance neighbors of measured anchors, negative results, and a
  weekly arXiv watcher. Distances and ranks are retrieval scores, not
  probability estimates of Tc.
